video_info.title: solo dates that changed my life

transcript.text: have you ever felt like you're trapped
in The Daily Grind when's the last time
you take yourself on a solo date to
truly reconnect with yourself a book
called The Artist way recently
transformed my life one of the task was
that I carve out an hour or two every
week just for me it can be trying
something new or rediscovering passions
and joy that were forgotten from
coloring learning to reconnect with my
body through dense or immersing myself
in the beauty of nature these gateways
to creativity and self-discovery have
become my weekly non-negotiable one of
the most fun artist date so far was
taking a nostalgic trip to my childhood
favorite museum it's not just about
finding time it's about finding yourself
and those birst of joy that remind us
who we are and what we love this is a
sign to take that step to explore to
dream to nurture and find courage to get
out of your comfort zone
